CSS free-for-all mode
This ffa mod is based on CSS:DM and you need maps only with Counter-Terror or Terror spawn points, but only one of this.
The different to normal maps is, that you have only one team and the round never ends, because there is no team winning the round. 
In fact you need some changes in the server config to disable team kill messages and sounds. It's also possible to remove counter or terror spawn points with the mod stripper, but it makes only trouble with your server.
It's also advantageous that it isn't round based and respawn all over the map after death.

OK, this is my first map. I think it came out very well, but i am sick of working on it. So i dont plan on updateing it unless there is a major problem found (it takes FOREVER to compile). I made it with fast action in mind, DM or GG or just a standard us vs you kind of match. There are 15 spawn points for each side. I made a underground area (ladders into both CT and T spawns), and there are a few walls that you can walk through, but i dont think the games will last long enough for anyone to camp there... BTW, this is a very fun snipper map.

To save time, i have uploaded pics taken in a map viewer and not CSS, so the lighting quality and texture quality is way down.

Due to my mapping n00bness, i havent placed any props on the map, other than breakable windows and doors.

*UPDATED* Map has been tweaked somewhat, being that the wall has been moved in to close the open space of the floor somewhat.  And with testing the map with a full 19 bots, it was definitely a framerate improvement over the slightly expanded version.

I saw fit to do so since this map has strayed somewhat from the original feel I was going for.  There is still the much more detailed version out there, but this particular version needed to run as smooth as it can be.

After the map had started to chug along with twenty people, I could maybe push for 24, but 32 just seems unreasonable and a pure slaughterfest.  It'll stay 20 people only.
